  				<h1 class="entry-title" data-content-field="title"><a href="/blog/2017/4/4/fnb6rffxocknmsnnkbwzkpeukhk3a6">HOTTREADS: Volume Twelve</a></h1>

          <span class="article-dateline">
            <span class="date"><a href="/blog/2017/4/4/fnb6rffxocknmsnnkbwzkpeukhk3a6"><time class="published" datetime="2017-04-23">April 23, 2017</time></a><span class="delimiter">/</span></span>
