  				<h1 class="entry-title" data-content-field="title"><a href="/blog/2017/2/26/vixqjijz5nle4tzz6f09oj1dh099fk">Feelin' 32 </a></h1>

          <span class="article-dateline">
            <span class="date"><a href="/blog/2017/2/26/vixqjijz5nle4tzz6f09oj1dh099fk"><time class="published" datetime="2017-02-26">February 26, 2017</time></a><span class="delimiter">/</span></span>
