  <article class="hentry category-another-awkward-week tag-awkward tag-humor tag-nyc tag-funny-stories author-liz-scott post-type-text article-index-8" id="article-58a259d7d1758edfc7cd8df6" data-item-id="58a259d7d1758edfc7cd8df6">
    
