  				<h1 class="entry-title" data-content-field="title"><a href="/blog/2017/2/6/hottreads-2017-nonfiction-reading-challenge">HOTTREADS: 2017 Nonfiction Reading Challenge</a></h1>

          <span class="article-dateline">
            <span class="date"><a href="/blog/2017/2/6/hottreads-2017-nonfiction-reading-challenge"><time class="published" datetime="2017-02-06">February 06, 2017</time></a><span class="delimiter">/</span></span>
          </span>
          <span class="article-byline">
